This is a weather forcasting web application :
-> Made up of HTML CSS and JAVASCRIPT 
-> Also used API to get weather information and location 

->This application will store user location in sessionstorage and gives his current location weather report
->It also has search option that can help you to search to location for which you want know the weather


Weather application gives information about:
-- cityname  
--  country flag
-- tempreture in Â°C
-- windspeed  in m/s
-- humidity  in %
-- clouds  in %